name: Stevie J & Joseline Go Hollywood
overview: Look out, Los Angeles! Stevie J and Joseline hit the West Coast with their sights set on Hollywood stardom. With Stevie J's five children in tow - it's a family affair!

episodes.name: LA, The Stevie J Way
episodes.overview: Grammy award-winning producer Stevie J heads to LA on his own to produce his upcoming movie "That Time of the Month". Little does he know, his wife (and co-star) Joseline flew west as well.

episodes.name: The Truth Hurts
episodes.overview: Stevie has a secret to tell Joseline but struggles with how to drop the bomb. He’s worried about upsetting her while they are working on fixing their relationship.

episodes.name: The Jordan Clan
episodes.overview: Stevie J.’s kids arrive in LA. Will Joseline rise up as the International Superstar step-mom?

episodes.name: Joseline Goes PG
episodes.overview: Frustrated with her manager-husband, Joseline books a performance at a G-rated event in Los Angeles on her own. Can the Puerto Rican Princess keep it clean? And what will Stevie have to say about Joseline’s show?

episodes.name: Risky Business
episodes.overview: Joseline decides to find a new manager. Is Stevie too distracted to notice Joseline’s independence?

episodes.name: Take Me To Church
episodes.overview: Stevie is searching for peace in his family, but Joseline’s latest snub leaves the Jordans further apart than ever.

episodes.name: That Time of the Month
episodes.overview: Stevie and Joseline’s movie is back on track but the couple’s flawed relationship stands in the way of making a Hollywood blockbuster. Is the pair ready to forgive, forget and film?
